##Wuhan residents shouted "Fake" , the central guidance team moved to the real thing

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Jun Wang, thepaper.cn

The paper's chief commentator, XIPO

On the evening of March 5, CCTV news and Xinhua shared a common concern.

What's the problem? Prevention and control of epidemic situation and guarantee of people's life in Wuhan Community.

Central Guidance Team to the community

Xinhua news agency sent a telegram from Wuhan on the evening of March 5, saying that the community is the first line of epidemic prevention and control. In order to thoroughly implement the spirit of General Secretary Xi Jinping's important instructions and implement the deployment of the Central Leading Group for responding to the epidemic, the Politburo member of the Communist Party of China and Vice Premier of the State Council, Sun Chunlan, led the central guidance team to visit the Cuiyuan community in Qingshan district of Wuhan and the Xiqiao community in Kong Hon district to see for themselves the prevention and control of the community and the protection of people's livelihood.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Sun Chunlan asked about specific measures to prevent and control the community, learning about the work of community cadres, grid workers, sinking cadres, volunteers and so on. She stressed that Hubei and Wuhan Epidemic Prevention and control task is still arduous, we must continue to do a good job in community prevention and control work, firmly adhere to the joint prevention and control of the epidemic, mass prevention and mass control of the Community Line of Defense.

Sun Chunlan, who has detailed information on the supply of fresh vegetables, supplies for infants and children, and medicines for chronic diseases, asked the O to do a good job in providing services for living materials, enriching varieties as much as possible and optimizing distribution methods, we will strengthen support for people with disabilities, elderly people who are lonely or widowed, and other groups with special difficulties.

In response to the difficulties and problems reported by the masses on the spot, Sun Chunlan immediately asked provincial and municipal leaders to conduct in-depth investigations, not avoid contradictions, put an end to formalism and bureaucracy, and adhere to a pragmatic style of work, Seek truth from facts and solve problems in a practical way, the report said, improve the satisfaction of the masses.

On the evening of March 5, the CCTV news broadcast also reported the news of the Central Guidance Group.

What problems did the masses report?

In fact, the sentence in this important piece of news, "the difficulties and problems that the masses are reflecting on the spot, " contains a great deal of information. At 9:30 pm on March 5, "Tao ran notes" , a public wechat account, published an article titled "covering up contradictions can not solve the problem of livelihood security for the common people" with a more detailed disclosure.

Starting at noon on March 5, posts about the central guidance team's visit to the Wuhan neighborhood circulated online, both in text and video, according to Tao ran's notes.

On the morning of March 5, a resident shouted "fake, fake" from his window to the central guidance team during a visit to the Kaiyuan Mansion Complex in Cuiyuan community, Qingshan district, Wuhan, the Post said, the main reflection is the community property pretend to let volunteers send meat to the owners, the actual work is not in place.

The above-mentioned article said, according to Tao ran notes understand that posts about the scene of the content is basically true.

The article revealed that Vice Premier Sun Chunlan immediately asked provincial and municipal leaders to get to know the situation better and pointed out that it is normal for the people to have emotions, which reminds us that there are still shortcomings in the basic livelihood security of the people in the community. Don't try to cover up contradictions, try to Seek truth from facts them, make clear what the problem is, solve the problem in time and resolve the problem, and never engage in formalism and bureaucracy.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
How did the Central Guidance Group solve the problem?

Tao Ran Notes in the above-mentioned article pointed out that about 4 hours later, the Central Steering Group convened provincial and municipal responsible comrades held a special session. The study further does a good job of ensuring the people's livelihood, emphasizing to open up the "last kilometer" of the supply of living materials and community services, and do a good job of psychological counseling for the people in the community, so that they can live at home more safely.

Wuhan has sent people to the homes of more than 3,000 families in the community to investigate and resolve specific complaints.

"In the afternoon, the Central Guidance Group held a special meeting to study how to better ensure the livelihood of the masses, emphasizing the importance of getting through the 'last kilometer' of the supply of living materials and community services, and doing a good job of psychological counseling for the masses of the communities to make their home life more secure, " Xinhua said at the end of the cable

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Right away

#A fake is a fake, and a real voice is the most powerful

What it means to be a formalism and a bureaucrat, and how to get rid of it, was best illustrated in the March 5 issue of formalism.

"In response to the difficulties and problems reported by the masses on the spot, Sun Chunlan immediately asked the provincial and municipal leaders to carry out in-depth investigations, not avoid contradictions, put an end to formalism and bureaucracy, stick to a pragmatic style of work, Seek truth from facts and solve problems effectively, and enhance the satisfaction of the masses, " the report read

This is a very meaningful expression of public opinion and Response to public opinion. The central guidance team went to the front line to investigate in order to understand the real situation and solve the real problems. Fraud was both a distraction to the public and a distraction from the work of the Steering Group, and fortunately there was that loud and clear cry from instinct, which betrayed everything.

Through the network can only understand half of the story, that is, how the public voice, "news broadcast" the other half of the story complete. Now we know that the difficulties and problems reflected by the masses "on the spot" will be heard "immediately" and solved promptly and systematically. According to the official account of Tao ran's notes on Wechat, about four hours later, the Central Guidance Group convened a special meeting of the relevant responsible comrades of provinces and cities to study how to further ensure the livelihood of the masses, emphasis should be put on getting through the "last mile" of supply of living materials and community service, doing well the psychological counseling work of the community masses, and making their home life more secure. That's the right way to deal with public opinion.

Shouting from the top of the stairs is certainly an atypical expression of public opinion, but it's expensive in truth. As it turns out, the real voice is the most powerful voice, the one most needed for decision making.

On Wuhan residents should complain about the difficulties in life, there has been some controversy, some people say that we are not easy, we should understand each other. But only when public opinion is fully expressed can we know which issues need to be addressed first. Unity can only be achieved if all parties can share their aspirations, grievances and capabilities with each other. Let the conflict come to the surface, and the solution to the problem will emerge.

Epidemic situation is a mirror, all people, all things clearly, really not false, false really not. From the beginning of the epidemic to the present, from Wuhan, Hubei to the country, each link in each job to do, the public has always known. For those who sacrifice dedication, people have never been stingy praise, for those who make trouble, people will be directly exposed and vilified. In the end, all it takes is to get back to the Seek truth from facts.
